<p>We are looking for a <strong>open source</strong> solution for <strong>proxing traffic</strong> (<strong>via VPN</strong>) with support <strong>flexible rules system</strong>, with <strong>multi-user support</strong>. From a functional need to:</p>  <ol> <li>a ban on the proxy domain, or a regular expression links</li> <li>ban IP addresses</li> <li>the ability to block specific references on the mask (regexp), and not the entire domain</li> <li>api for adding, deleting and blocking user</li> </ol>  <p>There is a ready-made solution?</p>